									= link_to "Zack Pride", "http://zackpride.com/", target: "_blank"
									|, Bassist & Professor of Jazz Bass at George Mason University
				.carousel-item data-bs-interval="10000"
					.row.justify-content-center.pt-5.pb-5
						.col-lg-10
							.quote
								= image_tag 'icons/icon-quote.svg', :class=>"img-fluid", alt: 'quote'
								p.lead
									| "Working with Vanessa was an absolute joy! She was very attentive, knowledgeable, patient, and very timely! I was so nervous to just have anyone create my website but I am beyond pleased with Vanessa's work. She really listened to all my likes and dislikes to create exactly what I wanted and what my business needed! If you're a business owner in need of design, branding, or website creation Vanessa is your ideal person! I can't recommend her enough."
